// 3. BUILT-IN FUNCTIONS
Int current_date = Today();
Int release_date = 1774994400;
/$

## Metadata
Compiled by: ${author}
Version: ${version_major}.0
Build time: ${build_time} seconds

## Glossary Usage
$$ Req(MDS)
